# Sourced script: do-usrhome  -*- mode: sh; -*-
#
# Purpose   : Change current directory to USRHOME root.
# Created   : Thursday, March 28 2024.
# Author    : Pierre Rouleau <prouleau001@gmail.com>
# Time-stamp: <2024-04-06 10:53:31 EDT, updated by Pierre Rouleau>
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Module Description
# ------------------
#
# Change current directory to the root of the USRHOME and set the terminal
# title to USRHOME.

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Dependencies
# ------------
#
# - Invoked via: usrhome, an alias set inside usrhome/ibin/setfor-zsh-alias

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Code
# ----
#
#

cd $USRHOME_DIR/$1
set-title USRHOME

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
